    "This information is important for the decision makers to assess the company's profile and make decisions whether the company will be successful or fail.",
    "The below paragraph shows the formula to measure profitability, liquidity, efficiency and solvency of the business firm (Lukason and Käsper 2017).",
    "Business firms use social media platforms, like Twitter and Facebook, to promote their products or services to the public (Antretter et al. 2019).",
